{"tid":2162619,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［真.中共高層激烈內鬥］前黨校教授指責習近平‘弒國者’","createTime":"2020-08-18T08:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T13:24:47.000Z","uid":199800,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b0e54160053ac4eb8d46bef4e7643a91fbb160","tid":2162619,"uid":199800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:21:30.000Z","msg":"重點：<br />\n<br />\n-蔡霞係國家行政學院（一間培養中共高官嘅黨校）嘅退休教授，8月17日因為youtube一段佢批評習近平嘅錄音流出所以被開除黨籍。<br />\n<br />\n-蔡霞指控習近平<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">&ldquo;謀殺國家&rdquo;</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n-佢接受英國衛報訪問嘅時候話：佢相信佢果代經歷鄧小平改革開放時代入黨嘅人，特別係高級幹部都好不滿習近平，因為習令全世界與中國為敵。好多佢嘅朋友見到佢被開除黨籍都為佢歡呼慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n-佢話雖然黨內有好多不滿聲音，但好多人因為驚秋後算賬/被扣上貪污帽子所以唔敢出聲。<br />\n<br />\n-佢特別批評中共將武漢肺炎爆發嘅責任推卸到地方官員身上，但其實<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">責任主要係喺習近平身上</span></span>。根據黨刊《求是》（由鄧小平創立）嘅公開對話，喺‪1月20號‬國家公布肺炎具傳染性之前，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">習早已喺‪1月7號‬向政治局下令準備應對方案</span></span>，證明佢因為意圖壓下疫情而將消息推遲兩星期向公眾公布。<br />\n<br />\n刁大大眾叛親離<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死期近了<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/18/china-xi-jinping-facing-widespread-opposition-in-his-own-party-claims-insider?CMP=Share_iOSApp_Other\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2020%2Faug%2F18%2Fchina-xi-jinping-facing-widespread-opposition-in-his-own-party-claims-insider%3FCMP%3DShare_iOSApp_Other&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkFwvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=1742e309\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/aug/18/china-xi-jinping-facing-widespread-opposition-in-his-own-party-claims-insider?CMP=Share_iOSApp_Other</a>"},{"pid":"dc411b249c58714098492de3bf8282acd7e31529","tid":2162619,"uid":199800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b17c7c4b85021921d844aa474f1aaa88dbf95803","tid":2162619,"u